data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in Petal, MS! This stunning 5 bed, 3.5 bath residence with a brand-new master suite addition is a masterpiece of modern rustic design. Nestled on almost 7 acres in the top-rated school district, this home is a sanctuary of comfort and style. As you enter, you're greeted by a vaulted ceiling in the living room that adds an airy elegance to the space. The wrap-around porch beckons you to unwind and enjoy the serenity of your expansive yard. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or watching the sunset from the comfort of your own screened porch. The heart of this home is the brand-new master suite, a luxurious retreat with all the amenities you could desire. The attention to detail is evident in every corner, from the carefully chosen finishes to the...... spacious layout. Two water heaters ensure that you'll never run out of hot water, offering comfort and convenience. The walk-in pantry in the gourmet kitchen provides ample storage for all your culinary delights, making meal preparation a breeze. The second master bedroom adds flexibility, perfect for guests or a growing family. Not to mention the additional 2nd floor bonus addition that could be a 6th bedroom, office, theater, or play room!
For the hobbyist or entrepreneur, the property boasts a large his and her shop, thoughtfully split to accommodate different needs. One side is finished out with air conditioning, providing the ideal space for a home office, studio, or workshop. With two carports, there's ample space for your vehicles and outdoor gear. Safety and convenience come together with a built-in gun safe in the bonus area, offering peace of mind and practicality. This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestylea perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm.

Don't miss the chance to make this haven yours. Schedule a showing and step into the future of gracious living in Petal's top-rated school district. Welcome home!
